<%= render AssessmentParticipationHeaderComponent.new(company: @assessment_participation.assessment.business.company) %>
<main class="bg-zinc-50 h-full pt-10">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pb-16">
    <div class="border border-gray-200 bg-white rounded-xl px-6 py-10 md:px-12 md:py-16">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-x-16 gap-y-9">
        <div>
          <h1 class="font-extrabold leading-7 text-gray-800 text-2xl">Hello <%= @assessment_participation.candidate.name %>,</h1>
          <div class="mt-6 text-gray-800 space-y-3 font-medium">
            <p>Welcome to our assessment</p>
            <p>Completing this assessment will help you showcase your skills and knowledge.</p>
            <p>Good luck!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h1 class="font-bold leading-7 text-gray-800 text-xl tracking-tight">A few things before you start:</h1>
          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3.5 list-disc font-medium text-base ml-7">
            <li>This assessment consists of <strong>
                <%= @assessment_participation.assessment.tests.count %> parts</strong>
            </strong> test. It will take approximately <strong><%= format_duration(@assessment_participation.assessment.duration_seconds)%></strong> to complete.</li>
          <li>The assessment is timed. A timer is shown per test or per question.</li>
          <li>Before each test there may be preview questions, <strong>be aware the timer for the test will have already started.</strong></li>
          <li>Please allow the use of your camera/webcam and do not leave full-screen mode. Snapshots will be taken of you periodically during the assessment. These measures are taken to ensure fairness for everyone.</li>
          <li>You are free to use a calculator, pen and paper.</li>
          <li>We recommend completing the assessment in one go.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 flex justify-end">
      <%= link_to setup_candidate_assessment_participation_path(@assessment_participation), class: "primary-button gap-x-2.5 px-7 py-3" do %>
        <span>Get started</span>
        <%= svg_tag "chevron_right", class: "size-3 -mb-0.5", "stroke-width": 3 %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>
</main>
